<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= asset_path('styles.css') %>">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= asset_path('slick.css') %>">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="<%= asset_path('slick-theme.css') %>">
  


  
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/slick-carousel@1.8.1/slick/slick.min.js"></script>
  <!-- Add this script within the head tag, below your existing Slick Carousel script -->
  <script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
      $('.slick-carousel').slick({
        dots: true,
        prevArrow: false,
        nextArrow: false,
        infinite: true,
        slidesToShow: 2,
        slidesToScroll: 2,
        adaptiveHeight: true,

      })
    });
  </script>
  

  <title>Matt Cruz Fitness</title>

</head>



<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
      <nav class="navbar">
          <!-- Logo -->
          <%= image_tag 'logo.png', alt: 'Your Logo' %>
          
          <!-- Navigation Links -->
          <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#hero">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">About Me</a></li>
            <li><a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a></li>
          </ul>
          
          <!-- Call-to-Action Button -->
          <a href="#" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
          
      </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <%= image_tag 'me.png', alt: 'Matt Cruz', class: 'hero-image' %>
          <div class="text-container">
            <h1>Get Lean, Get Strong, Get Ripped </h1>
            <p>Oh, and you can still have fun doing it.</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Take Action TODAY</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    

    <!-- Pain Points Section -->
    <section class="pain">
      <div class="pain-content">

        <div class="pain-text-container">
          <h1>Do any of these problems sound familiar?</h1>
          <ul>
              <li><p><%="Hard time losing weight"%></p></li>
              <li><p><%="Low energy levels"%></p></li>
              <li><p><%="Inconsistent workouts"%></p></li>
              <li><p><%="Inconsistent diet"%></p></li>
              <li><p><%="Not liking what you see in the mirror"%></p></li>
              <li><p><%="Stress and anxiety taking over"%></p></li>
              <li><p><%="Occasional fits of rage directed at the current state of the Marvel Cinematic Universe"%></p></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag 'sad.png', alt: 'Matt Cruz', class: 'pain-image' %>        

      </div>
      <h3>Have you felt so overwhelmed it's tough to keep going?</h2>
      <h4><%="Well don't give up just yet!"%></h2>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
        <div class="about-container">
          <div class="about-text-container">
            <h2><%="Hi I'm Matt"%> </h2>
            <h3>And I know you can do this.</h3>

            <p><%="I'm not here to sell you on the latest fad diet. I'm not here to put you on a 6 week beach body workout plan. I'm here to get you results that will last."%></p>
            <p>Some things you should know about me</p>

            <ul>
                <li><p><%="I'm a NASM certified personal trainer"%></p></li>
                <li><p><%="I'm an amateur natural bodybuilder"%></p></li>
                <li><p><%="I've been lifting for the past 10 years"%></p></li>
                <li><p><%="I was a collegiate offensive tackle at Carnegie Mellon University"%></p></li>
                <li><p><%="I'm a former Big 4 Consultant and worked for companies like Apple and Meta"%></p></li>
                <li><p><%="I studied Information Systems, Game Design and Animation (I made this website)"%></p></li>
                <li><p><%="I'm a gamer, mediocre guitarist and a sucker for a good Pixar movie"%></p></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="about-cta-button">
              <a href="#" class="cta-button">Get Started Now</a>
            </div>

          </div>
          <%= image_tag 'hi.jpg', alt: 'Matt Cruz', class: 'hero-image' %>
        </div>

    </section>

    <!-- What's In Store Section '-->
    <section class="whats-in-store">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Here's What's In Store For You</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>The Mindset of a Winner</li>
          <li>Confidence through Knowledge</li>
          <li>No more belly fat, big arms and a superhero chest</li>
          <li>Motivation, accountability, support and guidance</li>
          <li>A flexible workout schedule catered to your lifestyle</li>
          <li>Reasons why the soft reboot will be a good thing for the MCU</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  
    <!-- Testimonials Section with Slick Carousel -->
    <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What My Clients Say</h2>
    
        <!-- Slick Carousel -->
        <div class="slick-carousel">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <%= image_tag 'johnny.jpg', alt: "Client 1's Transformation" %>
            <p><strong>Johnny</strong></p>
            <p>Before starting I often felt pretty sluggish and depressed. My lack of diet strategy and habitual exercise left me brain-fogged and I found it hard to get to the gym since I didn’t feel confident in structuring my own workouts.</p>

            <p>I was looking for a push and some educated guidance and I feel like MCF’s program has been exactly what I needed. The confidence boost of going into every day with a plan has been a great motivator.</p>

            <p>Coach Matt is also there literally every step of the way, super responsive, helpful, and flexible to answer my questions, meet my needs, and tailor the program specifically to me.</p>

            <p>I’m not gonna lie, I’ve been seeing results a lot faster and more evidently than I ever have before. I never tried to take pictures of my body at different timepoints, one because it felt vain and two because I was pessimistic about seeing any results. Matt has been persistent with getting me to track myself regularly, which has helped me notice changes in body shape which have been really amazing to see. Even more importantly, I’m loving my improved physical and mental performance as a result of consistent workouts and intelligent eating. I’ve felt more confident than I possibly ever have. All that’s to say I’m proud of where I’m at already and I’m only just over a month in.</p>

          </div>
    
          <div class="testimonial">
            <%= image_tag 'sample2.jpeg', alt: "Client 2's Transformation" %>
            <p><strong>Client 2</strong></p>
            <p>Matts guidance changed my life!</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="testimonial">
            <%= image_tag 'sample2.jpeg', alt: "Client 2's Transformation" %>
            <p><strong>Client 3</strong></p>
            <p>Matts guidance changed my life!</p>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial">
            <%= image_tag 'sample2.jpeg', alt: "Client 2's Transformation" %>
            <p><strong>Client 4</strong></p>
            <p>Matts guidance changed my life!</p>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial">
            <%= image_tag 'sample2.jpeg', alt: "Client 2's Transformation" %>
            <p><strong>Client 5</strong></p>
            <p>Matts guidance changed my life!</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Add more testimonials as needed -->
    
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Form Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="contact">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    
        <%= form_with(url: contact_us_create_path, method: :post) do |form| %>
          <div>
            <%= form.label :full_name, 'Full Name' %>
            <%= form.text_field :full_name %>
          </div>
    
          <div>
            <%= form.label :email, 'Email' %>
            <%= form.email_field :email %>
          </div>
    
          <div>
            <%= form.label :reason, 'Reason for Contact' %>
            <%= form.text_area :reason %>
          </div>
    
          <%= form.submit 'Submit' %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Matt Cruz Fitness. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

  

</body>
</html>
